parse

public static Session parse(java.lang.String uri)
                     throws java.lang.IllegalStateException,
                            java.io.IOException
Configures a Session according to the given URI. Here are some examples of URIs that can be used to configure a Session:
  • rtsp://xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx:8086?h264&flash=on
  • rtsp://xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx:8086?h263&camera=front&flash=on
  • rtsp://xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx:8086?h264=200-20-320-240
  • rtsp://xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx:8086?aac

Parameters:
uri - The URI
Returns:
A Session configured according to the URI
Throws:
java.lang.IllegalStateException
java.io.IOException
